snippet.title: Ace of Spades trailer
snippet.description:
ACE of SPADES is a game where you build to survive. Multiple objective based games modes, 32-players online, oh yeah, TOTALLY FREE. Been playing my self for quite awhile, take my word, It's AWESOME.

www.buildandshoot.com

Tag online is Shadz if ya see me say whats up =D usually green and building.
